  "description": "<p>Perched on the cliffs of the Amalfi Coast, this retreat pairs sweeping Mediterranean views with quiet, sunlit interiors. Wake up to the sound of the sea and unwind on a private terrace shaded by lemon trees.</p><p>The villa was thoughtfully restored to keep its original stonework while adding the comforts of a modern stay. Open spaces flow toward the water, making every room feel connected to the coastline outside.</p><p>Within a short walk you will find harbor cafes, hidden coves, and trails that wind through terraced gardens. It is an ideal base for travelers who want both seclusion and easy access to the heart of Amalfi.</p>",
